Welcome to my Platine Builder
This is a simulation for the old japanese mystery "Hashiwokakero"
This code is for the IT talent competition December 2017

This is an android application
The code can be imported directly to the framework Android Studio
The folder release_platine_builder_v4 includes the release built .apk file.
or to download under this dropbox link https://www.dropbox.com/s/rfy5o1agxgfvn54/app-release-platine-builder-v4.apk?dl=0
To run the application, please download the .apk file, an android
system (phone or simulator) will automatically ask you to install the application

I hope you enjoy my application. For further information, feel free to contact me
